title: VMware vCenter Server Appliance: CPU, Memory and Swap Utilization
agents: vcsa_health
catalog: app/vmware
license: GPL-2.0-only
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the CPU, memory and swap utilization of a VMware
 vCenter Server Appliance (VCSA) using the appliance monitoring API.
 The data is retrieved by the special agent {agent_vcsa_health}.

 Upper levels on the utilization can be configured via the ruleset
 "VCSA resource utilization". The default levels are 80/90 percent.

item:
 The resource: CPU, Memory or Swap.

discovery:
 One service is created for each available resource metric.
